  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      R3 closes the class of client-side email-send fragmentation bugs by replacing 6 ad-hoc implementations with one canonical engine + 3 wrappers + 1 Code Page + 1 typed wrapper. The wrap-up task is the final quality gate before merge-to-master.

      Per task-create Step 3.7 protocol, the wrap-up has 7 sub-steps (run code-review, run adr-check, run repo-cleanup, update README, update plan, write lessons-learned, final verification).
