  <steps>
    <step order="1">Invoke `/code-review` skill on all R3 code (Waves 0–6). Capture report. Categorize findings: Critical / Major / Minor.</step>
    <step order="2">Fix every Critical finding. For Major findings, decide per-case (fix vs file backlog). Re-run `/code-review` until zero Critical remain.</step>
    <step order="3">Invoke `/adr-check` skill on all R3 code. Capture report.</step>
    <step order="4">Fix every adr-check violation. Re-run `/adr-check` until clean.</step>
    <step order="5">Invoke `/repo-cleanup projects/email-communication-solution-r3` skill. Review the report; approve removals (notes/debug, notes/spikes, notes/drafts directories); archive handoffs per skill convention.</step>
    <step order="6">Update `README.md`:
