      - All wave statuses ✅ (Wave 0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, Wrap-up)
      - Note any deviations from original plan
    </step>
    <step order="8">**Write `notes/lessons-learned.md`** capturing:
      - Project objective recap (1 paragraph)
      - What worked well (1–3 items)
      - What was harder than expected (1–3 items)
      - Key insights — specifically:
        * LegalWorkspace fork delta (only 1 true fork, not 5 — CLAUDE.md finding #9)
        * `sprk_communication_send.js` LOC underestimate (~1,150 LOC × 2 vs spec's ~600 — CLAUDE.md finding #7)
        * UQ3 strategy resolution (Wave 0 task 003 — chosen Internet-Message-Id retrieval approach)
        * Active PR #360 collision handling (Wave 6 tasks 086/087/088/091)
        * Wave 5 single-PR shape lessons (review burden mitigation)
        * Form Component Control swap (UQ1 resolution in Wave 2)
      - Recommendations for future R-class projects
    </step>
    <step order="9">**Final verification**: confirm every row in `TASK-INDEX.md` is ✅ (no 🔲 / 🔁 left). Confirm `current-task.md` shows "none / project complete". Confirm zero Critical findings in `/code-review`, zero violations in `/adr-check`.</step>
    <step order="10">Update `current-task.md`: project status → Complete; next action → handoff to `merge-to-master` skill.</step>
    <step order="11">Update `tasks/TASK-INDEX.md`: mark task 099 ✅ completed.</step>
  </steps>

